ots]]\n|-\n|align=center| 4 || <span style=\"display:none\">Gary Cutsinger</span>[[Gary Cutsinger]] (from Boston)|| Defensive end || Oklahoma State || \n|-\n|align=center| 4 || Pick traded to San Diego || || || \n|-\n|align=center| 5 || <span style=\"display:none\">Bill Rice</span>Bill Rice || End || Alabama ||\n|-\n|align=center| 6 || <span style=\"display:none\">Ray Pinion</span>[[Ray Pinion]] || Guard || Texas Christian ||\n|-\n|align=center| 7 || <span style=\"display:none\">Gus Gonzales</span>[[Gus Gonzales]] || Guard || Tulane || \n|-\n|align=center| 8 || <span style=\"display:none\">Clyde Brock</span>[[Clyde Brock]] || Defensive tackle || Utah State || \n|-\n|align=center| 9 || <span style=\"display:none\">Larry Onesti</span>[[Larry Onesti]] || Linebacker || Northwestern || Released\n|-\n|align=center| 10 || <span style=\"display:none\">Bob Moses</span>[[Bob Moses (American football)|Bob Moses]] || End || Texas-Austin || \n|-\n|align=center| 11 || <span style=\"display:none\">John Thomas</span>John Thomas || Guard || McMurry || \n|-\n|align=center| 12 || <span style=\"display:none\">Jack Collins</span>[[Jack Collins (American football)|Jack Collins]] || Halfback || Texas-Austin || \n|-\n|align=center| 13 || <span style=\"display:none\">Royce Cassell</span>[[Royce Cassell]] || End || New Mexico State || Injured In 1962 [[Rose Bowl Game|Rose Bowl]]\n|-\n|align=center| 14 || <span style=\"display:none\">Glynn Griffing</span>[[Glynn Griffing]]* || Quarterback || Mississippi || \n|-\n|align=center| 15 || <span style=\"display:none\">Ken Shaffer</span>[[Ken Shaffer]] || Tackle || Marquette || \n|-\n|align=center| 16 || <span style=\"display:none\">Billy Ray Adams</span>[[Billy Ray Adams]] || Fullback || Mississippi || Released\n|-\n|align=center| 17 || <span style=\"display:none\">Bill Miller</span>[[Bill Miller (defensive tackle)|Bill Miller]] || Defensive tackle || New Mexico Highlands || \n|-\n|align=center| 18 || <span style=\"display:none\">Art Perkins</span>[